trans-unit.source: Associates a well-known object type that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator with a remote endpoint that can process messages that are sent to a method on the type.
trans-unit.target: Knytter typen kjente objektet som er sendt til generatoren for Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) med en eksterne endepunktet som kan behandle meldinger som sendes til en metode for typen.

trans-unit.source: The ServiceType class is used to hold information that is specified on the command line to the [Soapsuds Tool (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5) through the `-types` argument.
trans-unit.target: Klassen ServiceType brukes til å inneholde informasjonen som er angitt i kommandolinjen den [Soapsuds-verktøyet (Soapsuds.exe)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/40f6f8c8-b80c-4e9f-a920-31bcd0cf45c5) via den `-types` argumentet.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> class with the object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> klasse objektet <xref:System.Type>som er sendt til generatoren for Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the WSDL generator.

Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> class with the URL and <xref:System.Type> of an object that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> klasse URL-adressen og <xref:System.Type>av et objekt som er sendt til generatoren for Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the WSDL generator.
The well-known endpoint that can process messages that are sent to a method on the object type that is specified in the `type` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Velkjente endepunktet som kan behandle meldinger som sendes til en metode for objekttypen som er angitt i den `type` parameteren.

trans-unit.source: Gets the object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Henter objektet <xref:System.Type>som er sendt til generatoren for Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The object <xref:System.Type> that the current <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> was created for.
trans-unit.target: Objektet <xref:System.Type>som gjeldende <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> ble opprettet setningen for.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets the URL of an object <xref:System.Type> that is passed to the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) generator.
trans-unit.target: Henter URL-adressen til et objekt <xref:System.Type>som er sendt til generatoren for Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL).</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: The URL of an object <xref:System.Type> that the current <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"></xref> was created for.
trans-unit.target: URL-adressen til et objekt <xref:System.Type>som gjeldende <xref href="System.Runtime.Remoting.MetadataServices.ServiceType"> </xref> ble opprettet setningen for.</xref:System.Type>
